This directory includes an OpenFlow controller that emulates a layer 2
switch.

             packet out
         .---------------------------------------.
         v                                       |
+----------+           +-----------+           +---------+          +----------+
|  switch  |  *    1   | packet in |  1    *   | routing |  *   1   | topology |
|  daemon  | --------> |  filter   | --------> | switch  | <------> | daemon   |
+----------+ packet in +-----------+ packet in +---------+ topology +----------+
  ^ 1    ^                       |                                    ^ 1
  |      |                       |                                    | topology
  |      `-------.               |                                    |
  v 1            |               |                                    v 1
+----------+     |               |   packet in(LLDP)                +-----------+
| openflow |     |               `--------------------------------->| topology  |
|  switch  |     `--------------------------------------------------| discovery |
+----------+                         packet out(LLDP)               +-----------+


# How to run

  % ./trema run -c ./src/examples/routing_switch/routing_switch.conf
